section.section:
At the end of the term of a commission, the commission is renewable for a 3-year term if the employer of the special police officer:
submits to the Secretary a renewal application on the form that the Secretary requires;
submits to the Secretary a complete set of the special police officer's legible fingerprints on standard fingerprint cards;
pays to the Secretary a fee to cover the cost of the fingerprint record checks; and
subject to paragraph (2) of this subsection, pays to the Secretary a renewal fee of $60.
